75375772_1022956675825301_633129466162622252_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uz2qjCmTm-0Q7kNvgF11B3h&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDt2xeO1aZHZ6Oq9NJkHNopXdtpsMe1TlqvKvmPUFMxxQ&oe=67405D8A"}, {"file_name": "Untitled (3).png", "id": "1046991213631359", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982712_1046991216964692_3378362859507971090_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VDzwAdrgxl8Q7kNvgG9Ea6I&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBO28aE2VjqRxG4PnjFHEimFXmdYrXiIvwMNTVLvJqlYQ&oe=674086D4"}, {"file_name": "Untitled (4).png", "id": "874238157577420", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035302_874238160910753_5831353201944310081_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=HgRjYqDcbqgQ7kNvgFezVBy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB0mji-ApzAI87FamzorIFbZmlO5aQRSDhBqVKGxGPIJg&oe=67405C0F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Monkey Fear", "keywords": ["Monkey", "Monke", "Gorilla", "MonkeyFear", "Monk"], "long_description": "Monkey Fear is an immersive VR experience that puts you in the heart of a thrilling game of tag like never before. As a nimble and agile monkey, you must navigate through a series of diverse and increasingly challenging levels, each with its own unique atmosphere and obstacles. From the dark, twisting passages of eerie caves to the dizzying heights of towering skyscrapers, and the haunting shadows of mysterious forests, every environment is designed to test your reflexes and wits. The game is all about speed, strategy, and survival. Use your surroundings to your advantage\u2014climb walls, swing from branches, and dart through narrow spaces to evade your pursuers. The fast-paced gameplay keeps you on your toes as you try to outsmart and outrun other players in a battle of nerves and skill.", "short_description": "Monkey Fear is an adrenaline-pumping VR game where you take on t